	+ "- Every 12th attack splashes all damage over 200 AoE\n" \
	+ "- Every 15th attack adds 0.5% attack damage permanently\n" \
	+ " \n" \
	+ "[color=ORANGE]Level Bonus:[/color]\n" \
	+ "+200 attack damage on 7th attack\n"
